data.description: Amazing Newer home in Bauxite school district!!!  First floor has large great room with an inviting fireplace to get cozy by and open to kitchen and dining. Granite counter tops with a farm house sink, pantry, lots of cabinets and gas stove. This amazing home has 4 bedrooms upstairs and 2 full bathrooms and one of the bedrooms has a wet bar area which this room could be a movie or bonus room.  The upstairs also features a locking half barn door to block off the stairs at the top.  There is a half bathroom downstairs as well.  This open floor plan opens to the back yard which features a 10 X 17 ft deck in backyard and the private deck also has gas hook up and TV hook up as well.  This beautiful home also has High speed internet. This gorgeous home is a must see!!!!!  You don't want to miss this one!!!  Call me or your agent to schedule a showing and lets make this your new home!!!  Wooden Play/Swing Set and Trampoline to convey with the house.
